== 设施 ==
=== 环保游客中心 ===

雷纳姆沼泽自然保护区也是环保{{le|游客中心|Visitor center}}的所在地，该中心设有[[太阳能光伏|太阳能板]]、[[雨水撲滿|雨水收集装置]]、自然采光系统和[[通风|通风系统]]以及地热交换系统。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rspb.org.uk/reserves/guide/r/rainhammarshes/about.asp|publisher=Royal Society for the Protection of Birds|title=About Rainham Marshes|accessdate=2006-12-30|archive-date=2006-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061130044644/http://www.rspb.org.uk/reserves/guide/r/rainhammarshes/about.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>该游客中心在2006年建成，耗资200万英镑，<ref>{{Cite web | title = RSPB Environment and Education Centre, Rainham | publisher = van Heyningen and Haward | url = http://www.vhh.co.uk/projects/rainham.htm | accessdate = 2011-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110930040541/http://www.vhh.co.uk/projects/rainham.htm | archivedate = 2011-09-30 }}</ref>并获得了包括[[英國皇家建築師協會|英國皇家建築師協會]]颁发的国家奖项共六项奖。<ref>[http://www.vhh.co.uk/awards_project.htm van Heyningen and Haward awards] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228105304/http://www.vhh.co.uk/awards_project.htm |date=2013-02-28 }}</ref>

游客中心内部设有咖啡厅、卫生间和母婴设施。<ref name=Thurrock />

=== 垃圾填埋场 ===
自然保护区以西的沼泽被用作伦敦和当地垃圾的掩埋场，由威立雅ES垃圾填埋场有限公司运营。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Rainham Landfill Site|url=https://www.veolia.co.uk/essex/veolia-essex/landfill-sites|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719194012/https://www.veolia.co.uk/essex/veolia-essex/landfill-sites|archive-date=2020-07-19|access-date=2020-07-19|website=Veolia|dead-url=no}}</ref>垃圾填埋场占地面积177公顷，每年接收量达150万吨。<ref name=":0" />垃圾中的有机物分解生成气体，[[甲烷|甲烷]]含量高达50%。这些气体通过管道收集，由当地的一座发电站使用。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Rainham Landfill Gas Power Station|url=https://edlenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/EDL-Fact-Sheet-Rainham_Final.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720125032/https://edlenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/EDL-Fact-Sheet-Rainham_Final.pdf|archive-date=2020-07-20|access-date=2020-07-19|website=EDL Energy|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 游览 ==
=== 开放时间 ===
雷纳姆沼泽自然保护区的开放时间为11月1日至次年3月31日的9:30至16:30，以及4月1日至10月31日的9:30至17:00。圣诞节和节礼日不开放。<ref name=Thurrock>{{cite web|url=https://www.thurrock.gov.uk/rainham-marshes-nature-reserve/overview|title=Rainham Marshes Nature Reserve|accessdate=2020-09-12|publisher=thurrock.gov.uk|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007142752/https://www.thurrock.gov.uk/rainham-marshes-nature-reserve/overview|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== 交通 ===
旅客可以乘坐火车到{{le|珀弗利特站|Purfleet railway station}}，步行20分钟到达；或者乘坐44路到新坦克山路下车，公交车每小时一辆，高峰期半小时一辆。<ref name=guide />
